=== Implementation Notes ===

- Created tests/e2e/dedup_alignment_test.go with build tag e2e.
- Test injects 100k ticks with controlled duplicates (every 100th tick duplicated)
  through Manager.HandleTick, then compares CH row count vs injection count.
- Skips when E2E_CH_HOST is not set (CI-safe, no false failures).
- Full three-way reconciliation (metric/NATS/CH) is structured but requires
  the metrics endpoint (M10.3-2) and full pipeline wiring (M10.2-1/2/3).
  Current placeholder uses injected count; will be upgraded when /metrics is live.
- Error margin threshold: < 0.01% (matching ADR-0008 verification requirements).

